# ButtonA Filled

POCButtonA Filled is a button component federated as a module for POC on [issue #32](https://github.com/Infinisoft-inc/kitchen-next/issues/32).


## Filled Button

background-color: var(--md-sys-color-primary);
color: var(--md-sys-color-on-primary);
box-shadow: var(--md-sys-color-shadow);
font-size: var(--md-sys-typescale-large-size);
font-weight: var(--md-sys-typescale-label-large-weight);
font-family: var(--md-sys-typescale-label-large-family);

### Disabled Filled Button

background-color: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface);
opacity: 12%;
color: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface);
opacity: 38%;

### Hovered Filled Button

background-color: var(--md-sys-color-on-primary);
opacity: var(--md-sys-state-hover-state-layer-opacity);
color: var(--md-sys-color-on-primary);

### Focused Filled Button

background-color: var(--md-sys-color-on-primary);
opacity: var(--md-sys-state-focus-state-layer-opacity);
color: var(--md-sys-color-on-primary);

# ButtonA Outlined

POCButtonA Outlined is a button component federated as a module for POC on [issue #32](https://github.com/Infinisoft-inc/kitchen-next/issues/32).

## Outlined Button

outline-color: var(--md-sys-color-outline);
color: var(--md-sys-color-primary);
font-size: var(--md-sys-typescale-label-large-size);
font-family: var(--md-sys-typescale-label-large-family);
font-weight: var(--md-sys-typescale-label-large-weight);

### Disabled Outlined Button

outline-color: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface);
opacity: 12%;
color: var(--md-sys-color-on-surface);
opacity: 38%;

### Hovered Outlined Button

outline-color: var(--md-sys-color-outline);
background-color: var(--md-sys-color-primary);
opacity: var(--md-sys-state-hover-state-layer-opacity);

### Focused Outlined Button

outline-color: var(--md-sys-color-primary);
